com.ibm.team.repository.common.query

Interface IDataTypes


  • public interface IDataTypes

    Enumeration interface that defines int constants corresponding to all data query field types. Data query clients use these types for introspection of data query results.

    Since:
    0.5
    See Also:
    IDataRow
